*********************** WAITS ***********************

~Implicit wait is going to wait for the WebElement will generated
to be found until the timeout
driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(20,TimeUnit.SECONDS)
  1. declare them only once in the starting of your code----> global waits

~Explicit wait is condition wait(like wait for the webElement to be visible and
clickable).
